                              <h2 itemprop="name" class="small_h2_font">Pre-Opener</h2>
                              <div class="pro_name">Fiber opener machine for preliminarily opening and blending of fiber materials</div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-md-6 order-md-last">
                                        <figure>
                                            <div class="left_pro_img">
                                              <div class="left_pics">
                                                <a href="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_01.webp"><img itemprop="image" src="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_01.webp" alt="Pre-Opener"></a>
                                              </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="related_pic justify-content-center">
                                              <a class="imgdq" href="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_01.webp"><img src="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_01b.webp" alt="Pre-Opener"></a>
                                              <a href="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_02.webp"><img src="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_02b.webp" alt="Pre-Opener"></a>
                                              <a href="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_03.webp"><img src="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_03b.webp" alt="Pre-Opener"></a>
                                              <a href="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_04.webp"><img src="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_04b.webp" alt="Pre-Opener"></a>
                                              <a href="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_05.webp"><img src="products/1-1-2-pre-opener_05b.webp" alt="Pre-Opener"></a>
                                            </div>
                                          </figure>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p>
                                            Pre-opener is an important nonwoven machinery specifically designed for opening various fibers of short length. Its flexible design of opening cylinders allows it to be matched with different production processes.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="table-responsive">
                                            <table class="table"> <tr > <td  rowspan="2"  > Cylinder </td> <td  colspan="3"  > Cover with steel tooth / card wire / pin board </td> </tr> <tr > <td  colspan="3"  > ≤900 RPM </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Working width </td> <td   > 1000mm </td> <td   > 1300mm </td> <td   > 1500mm </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Capacity </td> <td   > ≤150kg/h </td> <td   > ≤300kg/h </td> <td   > ≤500kg/h </td> </tr> </table>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="request_btn request_btn1" onclick="openwindow('');return false">
                                          <notrans><span>Request Information</span></notrans>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="page_title">Functions</div>
                                <p class="mb-0">The pre-opener plays a crucial role in nonwoven manufacturing process by opening and preliminarily processing fiber raw materials, providing a high-quality fiber foundation for subsequent textile processing.</p>
                                <ul class="proitem ">
                                     <li>Opens fiber raw materials to reduce neps and entanglement between fibers.</li>
                                     <li>Aids in filtering impurities and preliminarily blending of different fibers.</li>
                                     <li>Suitable for opening all kinds of fibers, polyester, polypropylene, microfibers, cotton, jute, fiberglass, shoddy fibers, etc.</li>
                                </ul>
                                <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                <ul class="proitem">
                                   <li>The special air duct design prevents fiber blockage and improves reliability.</li>
                                   <li>Fiber pre-opener comes with emergency stop device, safety cover, reverse function, bridge magnet, etc., ensuring operational safety.</li>
                                   <li>Fully enclosed and integrated design greatly reduces dust leakage and flying flocks.</li>
                                   <li>The pre-opener allows for high-efficiency opening while minimum fiber damage.</li>
                                   <li>Optional device is available, such as oil/water sprayer according to customer needs.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </content>
