                                            </div>
                                          </figure>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p>
                                            Fine opener is specifically designed to open various short fibers for nonwoven fabric production. It employs different types of opening cylinders to open different materials and is typically used together with a pre-opener to achieve a good opening effect.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="table-responsive">
                                            <table class="table"> <tr > <td  rowspan="2"  > Cylinder </td> <td  colspan="3"  > Covered with card wire / pin board </td> </tr> <tr > <td  colspan="3"  > ≤900 RPM </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Working width </td> <td   > 1000mm </td> <td   > 1300mm </td> <td   > 1500mm </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Capacity </td> <td   > ≤150kg/h </td> <td   > ≤300kg/h </td> <td   > ≤500kg/h </td> </tr> </table>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="request_btn request_btn1" onclick="openwindow('');return false">
                                          <notrans><span>Request Information</span></notrans>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="page_title">Functions</div>
                                <ul class="proitem ">
                                     <li>Further opening of fiber raw materials to achieve thorough opening.</li>
                                     <li>Aids in filtering impurities and further blending of different fibers.</li>
                                     <li>Suitable for opening of various fibers such as polyester, polypropylene, microfibers, cotton, jute, fiberglass, shoddy fibers, etc.</li>
                                </ul>
                                <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                <ul class="proitem">
                                   <li>The special air duct design prevents fiber blockage and improves reliability.</li>
                                   <li>Fine opener comes with emergency stop device, safety cover, reverse function, bridge magnet, etc., ensuring operational safety. </li>
                                   <li>Optional device is available, such as oil/water sprayer according to customer needs.</li>
                                   <li>Fully enclosed and integrated design greatly reduces dust leakage and flying flocks.</li>
                                   <li>The fine opener allows for high-efficiency opening while minimum fiber damage.</li>
                                </ul>
