                              <h2 itemprop="name" class="small_h2_font">Fiber Mixer</h2>
                              <div class="pro_name">Mixing and proportion control of different fibers for nonwoven production</div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-md-6 order-md-last">
                                        <figure>
                                            <div class="left_pro_img">
                                              <div class="left_pics">
                                                <a href="products/1-1-4-fiber-mixer_01.webp"><img itemprop="image" src="products/1-1-4-fiber-mixer_01.webp" alt="Fiber Mixer"></a>
                                              </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="related_pic justify-content-center">
                                              <a class="imgdq" href="products/1-1-4-fiber-mixer_01.webp"><img src="products/1-1-4-fiber-mixer_01b.webp" alt="Fiber Mixer"></a>
                                              <a href="products/1-1-4-fiber-mixer_02.webp"><img src="products/1-1-4-fiber-mixer_02b.webp" alt="Fiber Mixer"></a>
                                              <a href="products/1-1-4-fiber-mixer_03.webp"><img src="products/1-1-4-fiber-mixer_03b.webp" alt="Fiber Mixer"></a>
                                            </div>
                                          </figure>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p>
                                            Fiber mixer, as a type of nonwoven machinery, typically consists of a weighing system and mixing beaters. It is used to mix various fiber raw materials into a uniform fiber blend for use in subsequent production processes.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="table-responsive">
                                            <table class="table"> <tr > <td   > Working width </td> <td  colspan="2"  > 1000mm-1500mm </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Beaters </td> <td   > 3 Beaters </td> <td   > 5 Beaters </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Category </td> <td   > Monomer </td> <td   > Storage Integrated </td>  </tr> </table>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="request_btn request_btn1" onclick="openwindow('');return false">
                                          <notrans><span>Request Information</span></notrans>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="page_title">Functions</div>
                                <ul class="proitem ">
                                     <li>Weighing different types of fibers according to specified proportions.</li>
                                     <li>Quantitatively blending different fibers together.</li>
                                     <li>Optionally equipped with fiber storage function, and feeding them to the next process if needed.</li>
                                </ul>
                                <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                <ul class="proitem">
                                   <li>Fiber mixer supports accurate weighing and quantitative feeding of materials for blending, ensuring a fixed proportion of fiber blend.</li>
                                   <li>The blending speed and time are adjustable, allowing for online control and coordination with the speeds of preceding and subsequent equipment.</li>
                                   <li>The uniformity of blending is greatly improved compared to a regular fiber mixing machine.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </content>
