                                <h2 itemprop="name" class="small_h2_font" data-title="Fiber Opening & Blending">Fiber Opening & Blending Equipment</h2>
                                <div class="pro_name">Fiber preparation machines of nonwoven production line</div>
                                <p>
                                  In the nonwoven manufacturing process, opening and blending are the primary processes involved, which include opening, removing impurities, blending, mixing different fibers, and related treatments. A wide variety of fibers can be utilized in nonwoven production, including conventional synthetic and man-made fibers, natural fibers, and even some recycled fibers.
                                </p>
