                                  </div>
                                  <div class="pro_des">
                                    <a href="1-1-1-bale-opener.html">Bale Opener</a>
                                    <p>The bale opener is one of the fiber opening devices, primarily used for the opening of fiber bales and weighing and proportioning of various fibers. Different raw material mixtures can be set by the collaborative work of multiple bale openers.</p>
                                    <div class="spec_list">
                                      <dl>Working width: 1100mm, 1400mm, 1500mm</dl>
                                      <dl>Capacity: ≤200kg/h, ≤300kg/h, ≤350kg/h</dl>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                  </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                  <div class="pro_img">
