                                    <a href="1-1-2-pre-opener.html">Pre-Opener</a>
                                    <p>Pre-opener is an important nonwoven machinery specifically designed for opening various fibers of short length. Its flexible design of opening cylinders allows it to be matched with different production processes.</p>
                                    <div class="spec_list">
                                      <dl>Working width: 1000mm, 1300mm, 1500mm</dl>
                                      <dl>Capacity: ≤150kg/h, ≤300kg/h, ≤500kg/h</dl>
                                    </div>
                                  </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                  <div class="pro_img">
                                    <a href="1-1-3-fine-opener.html"><img src="products/1-1-3-fine-opener_01b.webp" alt="Fine Opener"></a>
                                  </div>
                                  <div class="pro_des">
                                    <a href="1-1-3-fine-opener.html">Fine Opener</a>
                                    <p>Fine opener is specifically designed to open various short fibers for nonwoven fabric production. It employs different types of opening cylinders to open different materials and is typically used together with a pre-opener to achieve a good opening effect.</p>
                                    <div class="spec_list">
                                      <dl>Working width: 1000mm, 1300mm, 1500mm</dl>
                                      <dl>Capacity: ≤150kg/h, ≤300kg/h, ≤500kg/h</dl>
                                    </div>
                                  </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                  <div class="pro_img">
                                    <a href="1-1-4-fiber-mixer.html"><img src="products/1-1-4-fiber-mixer_01b.webp" alt="Fiber Mixer"></a>
                                  </div>
                                  <div class="pro_des">
                                    <a href="1-1-4-fiber-mixer.html">Fiber Mixer</a>
                                    <p>Fiber mixer, as a type of nonwoven machinery, typically consists of a weighing system and mixing beaters. It is used to mix various fiber raw materials into a uniform fiber blend for use in subsequent production processes.</p>
                                    <div class="spec_list">
                                      <dl>Working width: 1000mm-1500mm</dl>
                                      <dl>Beaters: 3 Beaters, 5 Beaters</dl>
                                    </div>
                                  </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                  <div class="pro_img">
                                    <a href="1-1-5-automatic-blending-box.html"><img src="products/1-1-5-automatic-blending-box_01b.webp" alt="Blending Machine"></a>
                                  </div>
                                  <div class="pro_des">
                                    <a href="1-1-5-automatic-blending-box.html">Blending Machine</a>
                                    <p>As an important nonwoven machinery, automatic blending box plays a crucial role in thoroughly mixing various fibers within the blending box. This function significantly enhances the uniformity of the fiber mixture and allows for fiber storage to facilitate continuous production.</p>
