                              <h2 itemprop="name" class="small_h2_font">Vertical Lapper</h2>
                              <div class="pro_name">Fiber web to be folded in vertical form</div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-md-6 order-md-last">
                                        <figure>
                                            <div class="left_pro_img">
                                              <div class="left_pics">
                                                <div class="video_play" data-path="en/czshannuoke/video-vertical-lapper_en">
                                                  <span class="venobox play_btn vbox-item"><i class="icon-play"></i></span>
                                              </div>
                                                <a href="products/1-3-3-vertical-lapper_01.webp"><img itemprop="image" src="products/1-3-3-vertical-lapper_01.webp" alt="Vertical Lapper"></a>
                                              </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="related_pic justify-content-center">
                                              <a class="imgdq" href="products/1-3-3-vertical-lapper_01.webp"><img src="products/1-3-3-vertical-lapper_01b.webp" alt="Vertical Lapper"></a>
                                              <a href="products/1-3-3-vertical-lapper_02.webp"><img src="products/1-3-3-vertical-lapper_02b.webp" alt="Vertical Lapper"></a>
                                              <a href="products/1-3-3-vertical-lapper_03.webp"><img src="products/1-3-3-vertical-lapper_03b.webp" alt="Vertical Lapper"></a>
                                            </div>
                                          </figure>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p>
                                            Vertical lapper stacks the fiber web in the vertical direction, and the formed webs come with higher fluffiness and better upright resilience than fiber web produced by cross lappers. The final product exhibits superior physical elasticity, rebound, and shape stability compared to regular crosslappers.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="table-responsive">
                                            <table class="table"> <tr > <td   > Input width </td> <td   > 1500mm-2500mm </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Input speed </td> <td   > ≤40m/min </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Thickness adjustment </td> <td   > 50mm~2000mm </td></tr> </table>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="request_btn request_btn1" onclick="openwindow('');return false">
                                          <notrans><span>Request Information</span></notrans>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="page_title">Application</div>
                                <p>
                                  Vertical lapper is particularly suitable for making mattress padding or other upholstery nonwoven materials, nonwoven insulations, etc.
                                </p>
                                <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                <ul class="proitem">
                                    <li>Variable frequency speed control enables flexible production of products with various thicknesses and characteristics.</li>
                                    <li>Special transmission design eliminates the product deformation caused by drafting.</li>
                                </ul>
