                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p>
                                            Structuring needle loom is a type of nonwoven equipment used for post-processing of nonwoven fabric products. It has evolved from conventional needle punching technology and aims to enhance the appearance and performance of products. <br>
                                            Depending on different production process requirements, this type of nonwoven equipment can be divided into various types, including structuring needle punching machine, jacquard needle punching machine, and stripe needle punching machine, among others, to meet the production needs of different types of nonwoven products.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="request_btn request_btn1" onclick="openwindow('');return false">
