                              <h2 itemprop="name" class="small_h2_font">Thermobonding Oven with Single Conveyor</h2>
                              <div class="pro_name">Oven for making thermal bonded nonwovens</div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-md-6 order-md-last">
                                        <figure>
                                            <div class="left_pro_img">
                                              <div class="left_pics">
                                                <a href="products/1-5-1-thermobonding-oven_01.webp"><img itemprop="image" src="products/1-5-1-thermobonding-oven_01.webp" alt="Thermobonding Oven with Single Conveyor"></a>
                                              </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="related_pic justify-content-center">
                                              <a class="imgdq" href="products/1-5-1-thermobonding-oven_0.webp"><img src="products/1-5-1-thermobonding-oven_0b.webp" alt="Thermobonding Oven with Single Conveyor"></a>
                                              <a href="products/1-5-1-thermobonding-oven_01.webp"><img src="products/1-5-1-thermobonding-oven_01b.webp" alt="Thermobonding Oven with Single Conveyor"></a>
                                              <a href="products/1-5-1-thermobonding-oven_02.webp"><img src="products/1-5-1-thermobonding-oven_02b.webp" alt="Thermobonding Oven with Single Conveyor"></a>
                                            </div>
                                          </figure>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p>
                                            Thermalbonding oven, belong to the nonwoven equipment, utilizes the process of hot air penetration to heat the fiber web containing low-melting point fibers, thus achieving the bonding and reinforcement of the fiber web, resulting in the formation of bonded fiber web.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="spec_list">
                                            <dl><b>Working width:</b> 2300mm～4000mm</dl>
                                            <dl><b>Available products weight:</b> 100～600 GSM</dl>
                                            <dl><b> Heating area:</b>  6 – 10 meters (customization) </dl>
                                          </div>
                                        <div class="request_btn request_btn1" onclick="openwindow('');return false">
                                          <notrans><span>Request Information</span></notrans>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="page_title">Application</div>
                                <p>Thermalbonding oven is used in nonwoven production lines and is suitable for producing various soft and low GSM products, such as thermal bonded wadding, fillers, insulation materials, etc.</p>
                                <div class="page_title">Specifications</div>
                                <div class="table-responsive">
                                    <table class="table"> <tr > <td   > Working width </td> <td   > 2300mm～4000mm </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Available products weight </td> <td   > 100～600 GSM </td> </tr> <tr > <td  rowspan="3"  > Optional Heating method </td> <td   > Boiler with thermal oil </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Burner (gas, diesel, LPG etc) </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Electrical radiator </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Structure features </td> <td   > Single floor ; Single conveyor </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Heating area </td> <td   > 6 – 10 meters (customization) </td> </tr> </table>
                                </div>
                                <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                <ul class="proitem">
                                    <li>Thermobonding oven comes with a single-layer structure with two separate upper and lower hot air channels.</li>
                                    <li>Circular airflow allows for efficient and uniform heating, resulting in excellent product quality.</li>
                                    <li>Functions include automatic and precise temperature control, independently adjustable air volume and heating power.</li>
                                    <li>Multiple insulation design helps in energy saving.</li>
                                    <li>Optional heating methods are burner, boiler, electric heating.</li>
                                </ul>
