                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p>
                                          Spray/chemical bonding oven is a versatile nonwoven equipment used to heat fiber webs and achieve bonding and drying, making it applicable for producing chemical bond wadding and thermal bond wadding as well. 
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="spec_list">
                                            <dl><b>Working width:</b> 2300mm～40000mm</dl>
                                            <dl><b>Referenced products weight:</b> 60～800GSM</dl>
                                            <dl><b> Heating area:</b>  6 – 12 meters (customization)</dl>
                                          </div>
                                        <div class="request_btn request_btn1" onclick="openwindow('');return false">
                                          <notrans><span>Request Information</span></notrans>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
