                                <div class="page_title">Application</div>
                                <p>Spray/chemical bonding oven is used in the bonding and drying process of fiber webs in nonwoven production.</p>
                                <div class="page_title">Specifications</div>
                                <div class="table-responsive">
                                    <table class="table"> <tr > <td   > Working width </td> <td   > 2300mm～40000mm </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Referenced products weight </td> <td   > 60～800GSM </td> </tr> <tr > <td  rowspan="3"  > Optional Heating method </td> <td   > Boiler with thermal oil heating </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Burner (gas, diesel, etc.) </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Electrical radiator </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Heating area </td> <td   > 6 – 12 meters (customization) </td>  </tr> </table>
                                </div>
                                <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                <ul class="proitem">
                                    <li>Spray/chemical bonding oven comes with a three-layer structure with separate upper and lower hot air channel for each layer.</li>
                                    <li>Circular airflow allows for efficient and uniform heating, resulting in excellent product quality.</li>
                                    <li>Functions include automatic and precise temperature control, independently adjustable air volume and heating power for each heating layer.</li>
                                    <li>Multiple insulation design helps in energy saving.</li>
                                    <li>The spray quantity and speed are adjustable.</li>
                                    <li>Optional heating methods are burner, boiler, electric heating.</li>
                                </ul>
