                              <h2 itemprop="name" class="small_h2_font">Ironing Machine</h2>
                              <div class="pro_name">For surface finishing of nonwoven products</div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-md-6 order-md-last">
                                        <figure>
                                            <div class="left_pro_img">
                                              <div class="left_pics">
                                                <a href="products/1-6-2-nonwoven-ironing-machine_01.webp"><img itemprop="image" src="products/1-6-2-nonwoven-ironing-machine_01.webp" alt="Ironing Machine"></a>
                                              </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="related_pic justify-content-center">
                                              <a class="imgdq" href="products/1-6-2-nonwoven-ironing-machine_01.webp"><img src="products/1-6-2-nonwoven-ironing-machine_01b.webp" alt="Ironing Machine"></a>
                                              <a href="products/1-6-2-nonwoven-ironing-machine_02.webp"><img src="products/1-6-2-nonwoven-ironing-machine_02b.webp" alt="Ironing Machine"></a>
                                            </div>
                                          </figure>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p>
                                            In the nonwoven fabric processing process, nonwoven ironing machine serves as a post-processing device used for surface calendering treatment of nonwoven products to achieve a smoother surface. It is commonly used for producing thermal bonded wadding products.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="spec_list spec_list2">
                                                <dl><b>Working width:</b> 2000mm~4500mm</dl>
                                                <dl><b>Linear speed:</b> 1~25m/min</dl>
                                              </div>
                                        <div class="request_btn request_btn1" onclick="openwindow('');return false">
                                          <notrans><span>Request Information</span></notrans>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="page_title">Specifications</div>
                                <div class="table-responsive">
                                    <table class="table text-center"> <tr >  <td   > Category </td> <td   > Two rollers </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Working width </td> <td   > 2000mm~4500mm </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Linear speed </td> <td   > 1~25m/min </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Surface temperature </td> <td   > ≤220℃ </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Temperature variation </td> <td   > ≤+/-2℃ </td> </tr> <tr > <td   > Heating method </td> <td   > Electrical heating with Hermetic thermal oil </td> </tr> </table>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                <ul class="proitem">
                                   <li>Variable frequency control enables adjustable speed.</li>
                                   <li>Each heating roller can be independently adjusted for heating, with precise automatic temperature control.</li>
                                   <li>With high precision and hardness roller surface, rollers are heat-treated for durability and deformation resistance.</li>
                                   <li>Hermetic thermal oil or separate circulating thermal oil system can adapt to different types of production.</li>
                                   <li>Roller is coated with Teflon to prevent fiber adhesion.</li>
                                   <li>Overload protection, protective cover, emergency stop, and other multiple safety protections are equipped.</li>
                                </ul>
