                                            <li><a href="products/2-1-5-synthetic-leather-substrate-production-line_05.webp"><img src="products/2-1-5-synthetic-leather-substrate-production-line_05b.webp" alt="Synthetic leather substrate"></a><span>Synthetic leather substrate</span></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </figure>
                                </div>
                                 
                                <div class="page_title">Application</div>
                                <p>
                                    The needle punching nonwoven technology is primarily used to produce substrates for waterproof rolls, base fabrics for synthetic leather, and base fabrics for reinforcing layers of other composite materials. The products are applied in asphalt felt substrate, synthetic leather base fabrics, etc., with high added value.
                                </p>
                               
                                <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                <ul class="proitem">
                                    <li>Synthetic leather substrate production line adopts a high-end configuration to meet various performance requirements such as appearance, texture, uniformity, and strength of the products.</li>
                                    <li>Recommended configurations include multiple opening and blending processes, double cylinder carding machine, and high-speed needle punching to meet the production needs for high-quality products.</li>
                                </ul>
