                                            <li><a href="products/2-2-3-automotive-soundproofing-felt-production-line_04.webp"><img src="products/2-2-3-automotive-soundproofing-felt-production-line_04b.webp" alt="Insulation in automotive"></a> <span>Insulation in automotive</span></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </figure>
                                </div>
                                <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                <p>Automotive insulation felt production line configuration is flexibly adapted to different products and automation requirements. It mainly includes fiber opening and blending equipment, carding machines, web formation machines, web bonding and drying equipment, calendering and ironing equipment, slitting & winding machines, etc., to meet production needs, offering a diverse range of product specifications. </p>
