                                            <li><a href="products/2-3-2-scouring-pad-production-line_03.webp"><img src="products/2-3-2-scouring-pad-production-line_03b.webp" alt="Examples"></a></li>
                                            <li><a href="products/2-3-2-scouring-pad-production-line_04.webp"><img src="products/2-3-2-scouring-pad-production-line_04b.webp" alt="Examples"></a></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </figure>
                                </div>
                                <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                <p>The configuration of the scouring pad production is flexibly adapted according to different products and automation requirements. It mainly includes fiber opening and blending equipment, carding machine, web formation machine, needle punching machine, spraying device and impregnation device, oven, slitting & winding machine, and other nonwoven machinery, to meet production needs, offering a wide range of product specifications.</p>
