                                            <li><a href="products/2-3-3-impregnated-lining-fabric-production-line_03.webp"><img src="products/2-3-3-impregnated-lining-fabric-production-line_03b.webp" alt="Insole board"></a><span>Insole board</span></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </figure>
                                </div>
                                <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                <p>The configuration of the impregnated lining fabric production is flexibly adapted according to different products and automation requirements. It mainly includes fiber opening and blending equipment, feeding & carding machine, web formation machine, re-carding machine, impregnation device, oven, slitting & winding machine, and other nonwoven machinery, to meet production needs. Multiple carding processes can improve product uniformity, resulting in lighter weight and lower density in conventional products.</p>
