                                <div class="page_title">Application</div>
                                <p>Carpet backing line is mainly used in the post-processing of needle-punched nonwoven products in nonwoven machinery.<br>
                                    For nonwoven carpet products, back coating is generally required for curing after heating, while web bonding and drying treatment are applied to shape the products. <br>
                                    In addition, common geotextiles, synthetic leather substrates, shoe fabrics, and other products all involve post-processing procedures requiring width stretching and shaping.</p>
