                                        </ul>
                                    </figure>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="page_title">Features</div>
                                    <ul class="proitem">
                                        <li>The configuration of the carpet backing line can be flexibly adapted according to different products and automation requirements. Taking conventional nonwoven carpets as an example, there are various options for back-coating forms.</li>
                                        <li>The use of web bonding and drying ensures the quality of the product, with uniform shaping effects and excellent surface appearance.</li>
                                        <li>The length of the web bonding and drying oven, as well as the heating method, can be customized.</li>
