                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p>
                                            Textile waste recycling line consists of multiple opening machines, and the configuration can be tailored to the composition and condition of waste fabrics. These machines progressively open the fabric to achieve more thorough opening while controlling fiber damage. <br>
                                            This recycling line can be equipped with dust removal devices to maintain a clean production environment and fire alarm systems to enhance safety and reliability.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="request_btn request_btn1" onClick="openwindow('');return false">
