                                <div class="page_title">Application</div>
                                <p>Textile waste recycling line can be used for high-speed opening treatment of various types of waste woven or knitted fabrics, transforming them into their original fiber state. The opened waste fibers can be used to produce various nonwoven products or yarn spinning and weaving, promoting material reuse and sustainable development.</p>
