                          </span>
                        </h3>
                      </div>
                      <div id="collapse3" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="heading3" data-parent="#accordionExample" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                        <div class="card-body" itemprop="text">
                          <p>Nonwoven fabric has a wide range of applications in various industries, including automotive, apparel, home decor, construction, kitchen and bathroom, healthcare, environmental protection, and filtration industries, among others. As technology and product innovation continue to advance, the applications of nonwoven products are constantly expanding.</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                      <div class="card-header" id="heading4">
