                        <div class="card-body" itemprop="text">
                          <p>Based on the production process, common types of nonwoven products include needle-punched nonwovens, thermal-bonded nonwovens, chemical-bonded nonwovens, spunlace nonwovens, spunbond nonwovens, and meltblown nonwovens, etc.</p>
                        </div>
